{"tid":2251383,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"阿塞拜疆與亞美尼亞外長據報將到華盛頓晤蓬佩奧","createTime":"2020-10-20T18:25:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-20T18:44:58.000Z","uid":295230,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"e7be147df73ad8129f7f5e35c63ccde291c3aca4","tid":2251383,"uid":295230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T18:25:21.000Z","msg":"阿塞拜疆和亞美尼亞自上月底在納戈爾諾-卡拉巴赫地區衝突，雙方互相指責在簽署停火協議後，仍然發動攻擊。兩國外長據報將會在當地周五，前往華盛頓與美國國務卿蓬佩奧會面。美國國務院對此未有作出回應。<br />\n<br />\n路透社報道，亞美尼亞總統薩爾基相接受法國傳媒訪問時，指責土耳其支援阿塞拜疆，破壞地區穩定，同時亦不主張俄羅斯的軍事干預，令納卡地區成為「另一個敘利亞」。<br />\n<br />\n兩國衝突至今造成超過700人死亡。俄羅斯外長拉夫羅夫早前呼籲在納卡地區衝突各方，停止對抗思維。"},{"pid":"e7812a207155685e9c50d7284d661faf6b219c89","tid":2251383,"uid":30040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T18:30:30.000Z","msg":"美國：下？唔係應該見俄羅斯咩？"},{"pid":"10735f7b576079c82c29f0f06a57e8fc4cc25904","tid":2251383,"uid":295230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e7812a207155685e9c50d7284d661faf6b219c89","tid":2251383,"uid":30040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T18:30:30.000Z","msg":"美國：下？唔係應該見俄羅斯咩？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T18:33:42.000Z","msg":"見左2次"},{"pid":"847bff508bbd6c49f71fafa752956314c8dedfec","tid":2251383,"uid":310700,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T18:35:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/t0VDcs0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ft0VDcs0.jpg&h=62e0e336&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"535703d3c7b98263bf1ecead7d378db5924f381b","tid":2251383,"uid":59461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T18:38:47.000Z","msg":"呢個十月太多驚奇啦掛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ca72d675eb8db063c3e3d77c8c7a2edff027e66","tid":2251383,"uid":17359,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T18:42:14.000Z","msg":"去比元帥照肺？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6c5ca9a7c82bda06